            "zh-TW": "講者以一段幽默的開場白起頭，讓整個房間的人都放鬆了下來。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "Her e-mail was more humorous than his, so the team chose hers for the newsletter.",
          "highlight": [
            "more humorous"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "她的 email 比他的更幽默，所以團隊選了她的刊在通訊上。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "It was the most humorous presentation I have seen at this conference.",
          "highlight": [
            "most humorous"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "這是我在這場研討會上見過最幽默的簡報。"
          }
        }
      ],
      "synonyms": [
        "funny",
        "amusing",
        "witty"
